I have a tech doc that suggests that the default is BOTH sw 7 & 8 on = 50 Mhz 
clock.    Then it gives a table of settings that somewhat contradicts the 
statement about the default.  I gather that OFF / ON is 66 Mhz, although the 
doc implies 60 Mhz.   ON OFF is the other state, used for 90 and 120 Mhz 
chips.   

